    "date": "2023-08-04T15:03:02Z",
    "text": "Chance to Compete Act of 2022\n\nThis bill modifies examination requirements and other components of the federal hiring process for positions in the competitive service, including prohibiting examinations from consisting solely of a self-assessment from an automated examination, allowing for the use of subject matter experts to develop position-specific assessments, and requiring the creation of an online platform through which agencies may share developed assessments."
